Package: rho.http.httr2
Type: Package
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
Title: Httr2 Worker Transport for Rho HTTP
Version: 0.0.1.9001
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Sounkou Mahamane", family = "Toure",
           email = "sounkoutoure@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the Rho HTTP client contract with httr2 connections
    owned by mirai workers. Response heads and body chunks are relayed over NNG
    so HTTP parsing remains in httr2 and the calling R event loop stays
    responsive.
